    "ai_summary": {
      "summary": "Senator Farry's newsletter covers several recent activities: a committee approved his bill (SB 792) to double Pennsylvania's R&D tax credit cap from $60M to $120M; the full Senate passed SB 45 to increase penalties and consolidate laws around human trafficking; and the Senate passed a bill targeting medetomidine, a fentanyl additive. The newsletter also includes ceremonial items such as attending a local sports club centennial, welcoming an Eagle Scout to the Senate floor, and celebrating a local high school baseball championship.",
