      "summary": "Senator Farry's office forwarded PennDOT announcements about road and bridge work in Bucks County. The work includes high-friction resurfacing with lane closures on four state highways and a bridge rehabilitation project on Trevose Road that will require a full road closure and detour for approximately four weeks starting June 22.",
